		PowerGeneration = (&~/Part/Components/AreaCentralComponents/Components/AreaPowerProvider/HitEffects/0/TotalDrain) / (&~/Part/Components/AreaCentralComponents/Components/AreaRepeatingTrigger/Duration) / -1000
